  "title": "Rich Sweet Kenyan Apricot Tagine",
  "description": "A sweet and molten Kenyan dish featuring apricot jam, this tagine is perfect for a rainy day, and is shojin-friendly to boot. It simmered to perfection with a blend of spices and apricot jam.",
