  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the ginger and garlic and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Stir in the cumin, coriander, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the apricot jam and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
